Also there's a correction to make. Rampage is not a single attack, it's definitely a full round of attacks.<br>
<br>
Root used to steal rampage away, for some reason root procs and spells (like mage pets or Fist of Nature) would generate hate on the rampage list and let you move up it if you had such spells or weapons. That was fixed some time ago, I think when they changed root/stun to generate less hate.<br>
<br>
