<br>
This is why monks make great rampage tanks.  They are used to surviving anything.  They know that if they go out of range, if all else fails, they will stop taking rampage long enough for a CH to land.  Warriors are stupid.  They just stand there getting hit instead of going out of range of rampage in order to give time for the CH to land.  OK.  they aren't stupid but warriors are used to depending on clerics for surviving.  They don't think about what THEY can do in order to survive.  It is always what their healer needs to be doing to get them to survive.  Every time a monk gets CHed it is a shock to them even if they are the established rampage tank.<br>
<br>
Also if you ever find yourself as rampage tank, keep your damn agro LOW.  Nothing pisses me off more than the rampage tank suddenly getting main agro when the MT goes down.  <br>
